data.description: Nestled on a sprawling one-acre lot enveloped by mature trees, offering seclusion and privacy. A true haven, it boasts a full-length porch that extends the breadth of the home. The property caters to all your needs, featuring ample space to store your boat, park an RV, or pursue your hobbies in the large workshop. Step inside to discover an updated interior, wood-like floors, modern paint colors, and elegant trim. Natural light cascades through a magnificent wall of windows, illuminating the interior. The kitchen showcases a stone backsplash, beautiful cabinetry, and granite counters. Practicality meets luxury in the oversized laundry room, with generous counter space, a sink, and an abundance of cabinetry promise a harmonious blend of utility and elegance. Whether entertaining guests or finding solace in your personal haven, this home encapsulates the dream of a tranquil, secluded existence, harmonizing nature's embrace with modern comfort.
